@startuml

title E Visa Processing And Follow Up System State Transition Diagram

initial : Initial State

state "Logged Out" {
    state "Create Account" {}
}

state "Logged In" {
    state "Apply For Visa" {}
    state "View Status" {}
    state "Check Status" {}
    state "Cancel Application" {}
    state "Modify Details" {}
    state "View Details" {}
    state "View Purpose" {}
    state "Give Feedback" {}
    state "Log Out" {}
}

:Create Account -> Logged In : Login
Logged In -> Apply For Visa : Apply for visa, make payment and accept application
Apply For Visa -> View Status : View status after applying
View Status -> Check Status : Check status after viewing
Check Status -> Give Feedback : Give feedback after checking
Give Feedback -> Log Out : Log out after giving feedback
Logged In -> Cancel Application : Cancel application
Logged In -> Modify Details : Modify details
Modify Details -> View Details : View details after modifying
View Details -> View Purpose : View purpose of the application
View Purpose -> Log Out : Log out after viewing purpose

@enduml
